Output demo.gif

# Set up terminal
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

# Show current state
Type "git status"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "git add demo.tape"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

# Generate commit message
Type "comai generate"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Enter
Sleep 500ms

Enter
Sleep 1s

# Show the result
Type "git log -1"
Enter
Sleep 4s
